# Mage Ovale script based on SimulationCraft profiles
#
# Revision History
# 4.3.12 2012/01/04 - manaPercent() returns a percent, not a percentage, so don't scale it.
# 4.3.11 2012/01/04 - Tighten up the conditions for when to cast Conjure Mana Gem in Arcane spec.
#                   - Minor bug fixes to Arcane rotation.
# 4.3.10 2012/01/03 - Add more checks for if player has 4pT13.
#                   - Fix the suggestions for what an Arcane mage casts while moving.
#                   - Mirror certain actions from the Arcane burn cycle to the hover cycle that were missed previously.
# 4.3.9  2011/12/21 - Fix condition for minor burn phase in Arcane rotation.
#                   - Update Frost rotation to SC, T13H (r10506).
# 4.3.8  2011/12/18 - 4.3.2 fixes the maxMana() problem, so put back the exact condition for Mana Gem usage.
#                     Checkbox for having just one main icon or separate icons for burn and hover phases with a green/red
#                     visual aid for which cycle to use.
#                     Use Item() as the check condition for when an item cooldown is up.
# 4.3.7  2011/12/16 - maxMana() causes Lua errors, so use ManaPercent() instead until it's fixed.
# 4.3.6  2011/12/16 - Don't suggest hardcasting Arcane Blast while moving.
# 4.3.5  2011/12/16 - Use the proper name for the potion being used in the checkbox.
# 4.3.4  2011/12/08 - Move Combustion to the cooldown icon.
# 4.3.3  2011/12/08 - Checkbox for using potions.
#                     Coding style changes.
# 4.3.2  2011/12/08 - Fix error in how MANAGEMITEM was used, which was causing it to never be suggested for arcane mages.
# 4.3.1  2011/12/06 - Initial version based on Hinalover's contributed script.
#                     Use mage profiles from SimulationCraft, Tier 13H:
#                     Arcane (r10466): 4 icons - green/red for burn/conserve phase, burn rotation, conserve rotation, DPS CDs
#                     Fire (r10467): 3 icons - main rotation, DPS CDs, mana CDs
#                     Frost (r10466): 3 icons - main rotation, DPS CDs, mana CDs; checkbox for using Kuni's Frost PvE rotation

## defines ##

